Race.SpecificTitle: Alderman -- District B, Town of Jonesboro
Alderman -- District D, Town of Jonesboro
Jonesboro Fire Protection Dist. #1 -- $72.00 Parcel Fee - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Jonesboro Fire Protection District #1 Proposition
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Jonesboro Fire Protection District #1 levy, for a period of ten (10) years beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, a parcel fee on each parcel of immovable property as defined in Louisiana Revised Statute 40:1505(D) situated within the Jonesboro Fire Protection District #1 in the amount of $72.00 per year (an estimated $60,000.00 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) to be expended for the purposes of acquiring, constructing, maintaining and operating fire protection facilities and equipment including the cost of obtaining water for fire protection purposes and salaries of firemen, and all purposes incidental thereto?
